data.description: Step into this beautifully remodeled one-story home, where comfort meets style. Sunlight floods the welcoming living area, complementing the warm wooden floors. The dining space seamlessly transitions to the modern kitchen, featuring freshly painted cabinets and chic tile flooring. The expansive family room invites social gatherings and relaxation. Three bedrooms boast charming hardwood floors, with the master suite standing out, offering two closets and a convenient 3/4 bathroom. Your perfect blend of elegance and functionality awaits.
